{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "ee69d2bd-ed5a-4623-a346-11f4d8e47d49", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ee69d2bd-ed5a-4623-a346-11f4d8e47d49@1.pkg/1772597698821/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597699038", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ee69d2bd-ed5a-4623-a346-11f4d8e47d49@1.pkg/1772597698821/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597699038"}, "identifier": "ee69d2bd-ed5a-4623-a346-11f4d8e47d49", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题通过社区 &ldquo;蓝马甲&rdquo; 志愿者的事迹考查社会责任与生命意义的体现。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：志愿者积极融入社会服务，并非 &ldquo;远离纷争&rdquo;，A错误。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：参与公益，计较付出与回报错误，B不符合题意。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：志愿者主动融入社区，服务他人，而非封闭自我，C错误。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：符合材料主旨，志愿者主动承担社区责任，奉献中成就自我，D 正确。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选D。</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）&ldquo;蓝马甲&rdquo;是社区里的暖心符号。他们是独居老人的&ldquo;贴心儿女&rdquo;，是放学路上的&ldquo;安全卫士&rdquo;，是文明宣传的&ldquo;行走喇叭&rdquo;，是环境整治的&ldquo;清洁能手&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;社区蓝马甲志愿者启示我们（ ）​</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）“蓝马甲”是社区里的暖心符号。他们是独居老人的“贴心儿女”，是放学路上的“安全卫士”，是文明宣传的“行走喇叭”，是环境整治的“清洁能手”……社区蓝马甲志愿者启示我们（ ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ee69d2bd-ed5a-4623-a346-11f4d8e47d49@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977242956", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>明辨是非，远离社会的纷争​</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>参与公益，计较付出与回报​</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>封闭自我，专注个人的成长​</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>奉献自我，绽放生命的光彩​</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）&ldquo;蓝马甲&rdquo;是社区里的暖心符号。他们是独居老人的&ldquo;贴心儿女&rdquo;，是放学路上的&ldquo;安全卫士&rdquo;，是文明宣传的&ldquo;行走喇叭&rdquo;，是环境整治的&ldquo;清洁能手&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;社区蓝马甲志愿者启示我们（ ）​</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearnin